Hello, recently we have been getting a lot of Errors and Warning messages from our CAN’s, some of the problems we were getting are:

 "WARNING 1000 CAN Message is stale. talon fx 13 (rio) Status Signal SupplyCurrent" 
"ERROR 2 [CAN SPARK] IDS: 10,12, timed out while waiting for periodic status
"ERROR -1001 Could not transmit CAN Frame. talon fx 8 (Swerve_Carnivore) SetControl MotionMagicVoltage ERROR -1001 Could not tranmsit CAN Frame, talon fx"
"ERROR -1001 Could not transmit CAN Frame. talon fx 7 (Swerve_Carnivore) SetControl VoltageOut"

We checked the wiring of the CAN and everything seemed alright, and we are not exactly sure what causes these Errors or in what way, they could affect the performance of the robot.

We would really appreciate it if you could tell us the reason of the problem and a possible solution
